e Developers',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,9,6),(158,1,2,NULL,NULL,4,'https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/320193/000032019325000079/aapl-20250927.htm','ai-suggested','adversely impacting the CompanyÔÇÖs business, results of operations, financial condition and stock price.','BUSINESS',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,9,6),(159,1,2,NULL,NULL,5,'https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/320193/000032019325000079/aapl-20250927.htm','ai-suggested','If third-party software applications and services cease to be developed and maintained for the CompanyÔÇÖs products, customers may choose not to buy the CompanyÔÇÖs products, adversely impacting the CompanyÔÇÖs business, results of operations, financial condition and stock price.','The Company\'s hardware sales depend on the availability and quality of third-party software applications. If developers discontinue support or focus on competitors\' platforms with larger market share, customer demand for the Company\'s products may decline, adversely impacting financial performance.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,9,6),(160,1,2,NULL,NULL,2,'https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/320193/000032019325000079/aapl-20250927.htm','ai-suggested','Losses or unauthorized access to or releases of confidential information, including personal information, could subject the Company to significant reputational, financial, legal and operational consequences.','Data Security and Cyber Attacks',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,9,7),(161,1,2,NULL,NULL,4,'https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/320193/000032019325000079/aapl-20250927.htm','ai-suggested','could materially adversely affect the CompanyÔÇÖs business, reputation, results of operations, financial condition and stock price','BUSINESS',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,9,7),(162,1,2,NULL,NULL,5,'https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/320193/000032019325000079/aapl-20250927.htm','ai-suggested','attacks can impair the CompanyÔÇÖs ability to attract and retain customers for its products and services, affect its stock price, 