lities, regulatory challenges, inadequate returns, asset impairment, and failure to obtain approvals or counterparty performance.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,9,8),(165,1,2,NULL,NULL,2,'https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/320193/000032019325000079/aapl-20250927.htm','ai-suggested','The Company is primarily exposed to fluctuations in U.S. interest rates and their impact on the CompanyÔÇÖs investment portfolio and term debt.','Interest Rate Risk',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,9,9),(166,1,2,NULL,NULL,4,'https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/320193/000032019325000079/aapl-20250927.htm','ai-suggested','The Company is primarily exposed to fluctuations in U.S. interest rates and their impact on the CompanyÔÇÖs investment portfolio and term debt.','FINANCIAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,9,9),(167,1,2,NULL,NULL,5,'https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/320193/000032019325000079/aapl-20250927.htm','ai-suggested','Increases in interest rates will negatively affect the fair value of the CompanyÔÇÖs investment portfolio and increase the interest expense on the CompanyÔÇÖs term debt.','Fluctuations in U.S. interest rates can negatively affect the fair value of the company\'s investment portfolio and increase interest expense on its term debt.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,9,9),(168,78,1,211,NULL,2,'GET /api/stock/filing/78?accession=0001730168-25-000121&doc=avgo-20251102.htm','ai-suggested','Products','Products',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-06-08 08:38:10.673467',12,NULL),(169,78,1,211,NULL,0,'GET /api/stock/filing/78?accession=0001730168-25-000121&doc=avgo-20251102.htm','ai-suggested','$44,847','44847000000',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-06-08 08:38:10.673467',12,NULL),(170,78,1,211,NULL,1,'GET /api/stock/filing/78?accession=0001730168-25-000121&doc=avgo-20251102.htm','ai-suggested','70 %','70',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-06-08 08:38:10.673467',12,NULL),(171,78,1,212,NULL,2,'GET /api/stock/filing/78?accession=0001730168-25-000121&doc=avgo-20251102.htm','ai-suggested','Subscriptions and services'